Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.20,0:39:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.91,0:39:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向毒罐增加熱量\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Adding heat to the pressurized cannisters
