Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.28,0:39:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火藥和空氣中的氮的發生反應\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}between the powder and the nitrogen in the air
