Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.05,0:40:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Where's Gabriel?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.50,0:40:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.22,0:40:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和你女兒之間怎么樣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How did things go with your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.06,0:40:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興我去找了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm glad I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.76,0:40:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.06,0:40:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為  她長大了就會好一些\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I thought it would, uh, get easier as she grew older.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.48,0:40:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算我知道我做的是對的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But even when I know I'm doing the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.54,0:40:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也從未感覺對過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}it just never feels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.17,0:40:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能多說一句嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I speak freely?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.91,0:40:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒限制過你啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Were you not speaking freely before?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.28,0:40:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關于我媽媽的很多事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There are so many things about my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.55,0:40:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她有勇氣告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I wish she'd had the courage to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.90,0:40:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安  如果麗貝卡了解你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Lillian, if Rebecca knew you --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.43,0:40:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的了解你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean really knew you --
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.29,0:40:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會非常驕傲的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She'd be so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.35,0:41:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本想帶你去外面吃飯的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You know, I would have taken you to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.65,0:41:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就會錯過我手藝了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But then you would have missed my cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.95,0:41:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰教你做菜的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Who taught you to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.20,0:41:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一直煮了一手好菜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He always was a good cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.23,0:41:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他甚至為你的寶貝親手做飯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I mean, he even made your baby food himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.46,0:41:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  每當他生我氣時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yeah. He usually reminds me of that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.42,0:41:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他經常會提醒我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}when he's mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.30,0:41:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你畫完了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}So, did you finish your paintings?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.22,0:41:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了一張之外  你要看看嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Um...All but one. Do you want to see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.63,0:41:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不介意  我當然要看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sure, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.15,0:41:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.64,0:41:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麗貝卡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.84,0:41:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.21,0:41:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然記得  寶貝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.86,0:42:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然記得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.18,0:42:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得那天的每分每秒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I remember every second of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.95,0:42:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的  我知道經常令你很難受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Oh, honey, I-I know it's often been hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.43,0:42:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總是覺得從未真正了解過你的媽媽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You've always felt that you never really know your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.80,0:42:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為現在是時候改變了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I think it's time to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.78,0:06:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾·沃恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabriel Vaughn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我國戰功最卓著的士兵之一\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}One of our nation's most decorated soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是位英雄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's a hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而現在他是我們最秘密的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and now our country's most secret weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加布里爾擁有一種極其罕見的突變基因\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Gabriel possesses a rare genetic mutation
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我們能夠在他的大腦里植入微芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}That allowed us to implant a microchip in his brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.93,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將他的大腦直接與信息網絡聯通\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We connected his mind directly to the information grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是人類可望而不可及的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's something the chip does that nobody expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以在腦中重現事發時的虛擬場景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can create a virtual snapshot of an event in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并穿行其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and then walk through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是虛擬的證據墻一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's like a virtual evidence wall.
