Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星就位倒數  五\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Satellite in five.
